            <title><![CDATA[Little Nightmares Showcase set for June 24]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/06/little-nightmares-showcase-set-for-june-24</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/little-nightmares-showcase-set-for-june-24.1223214/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://www.gematsu.com/2025/06/little-nightmares-showcase-set-for-june-24<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div><p><a title="Companies > Bandai Namco Entertainment [6,706 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/bandai-namco-entertainment">Bandai Namco</a> will host a <em>Little Nightmares</em> Showcase on <a href="https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?iso=20250624T1900" target="_blank">June 24 at 12:00 p.m. PT / 3:00 p.m. ET</a>, the publisher <a href="https://twitter.com/LittleNights/status/1935729464823976221" target="_blank">announced</a>. <span id="more-974935"></span></p><p>The broadcast will feature the latest information on the <em>Little Nightmares</em> series.</p><p>Possible announcements include <em><a title="Games > Little Nightmares Enhanced Edition [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/little-nightmares-enhanced-edition">Little Nightmares Enhanced Edition</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [9,769 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [7,439 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [23,539 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a>, which was <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2023/12/esrb-rates-little-nightmares-enhanced-edition-for-ps5-xbox-series-and-pc">rated</a> in December 2023 and accidently released for PlayStation 5 on June 8 before being pulled from <a href="https://store.playstation.com/en-us/product/UP0700-CUSA05929_00-LITTLENIGHTMARES" target="_blank">PlayStation Store</a>, as well as the release date for <em><a title="Games > Little Nightmares III [5 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/little-nightmares-iii">Little Nightmares III</a></em>, which is due out for PlayStation 5, Xbox Series, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,105 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox One [14,037 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [17,254 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and PC via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1392860/Little_Nightmares_III/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Steam</a> in 2025.</p></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
